{"tid":2182420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中西區區議會］區議員問政府官員點解唔諮詢區議會就決定地點  官員： 唔關區議會事 之後離席","createTime":"2020-08-31T09:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T11:28:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"13f8f88c8105a75d9f1853fb4efe87c52228dfd8","tid":2182420,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"【即時：民政專員及所有政府部門人員離席】<br />\n<br />\n討論文件題為&ldquo;武漢肺炎「全民自願檢測」社區檢測中心選址接近民居 強烈反對在地區諮詢前開始計劃&rdquo;的文件。<br />\n<br />\n安排如何減少風險？防感染措施？<br />\n採樣人員細節？<br />\n用幾多公帤？<br />\n取樣時是否安全？<br />\n實驗室人員安排？<br />\n樣本如何運送？<br />\n如何消毒？<br />\n幾時會重開？ <br />\n<br />\n//根據《區議會條例》(香港法例第547章)第61條，區議會的職能包括就該條文所列明、關於有關的地方行政區的項目，向政府提供意見，以及在有關目的獲得撥款情況下，承擔有關的地方行政區的環境改善事務，康樂及文化促進事務及社區活動。<br />\n由於上述文件涉及的議題並非中西區地區層面的事宜，＃政府認為上述文件的討論內容並不符合《區議會條例》＃第61條所述有關區議會的職能。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1355027841303108/posts/1722022947936927/?vh=e&amp;extid=vXUvucGRvEZxYSsY&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1355027841303108%2Fposts%2F1722022947936927%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DvXUvucGRvEZxYSsY%26d%3Dn&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=a3883bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1355027841303108/posts/1722022947936927/?vh=e&amp;extid=vXUvucGRvEZxYSsY&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"16d18a67b9078bbaa677883d981d5841c3391dd1","tid":2182420,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">公職人員行為失當</span></span>"},{"pid":"80ffbc8de5155610dc591ea3ec0f76c8b0c8a630","tid":2182420,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dt0hDKK130&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0wy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=dbefb76a\" data-auto-link target=\"